---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<MainLayout title="Master Jason Gullion">
  <section class="profile-hero section-padding bg-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="profile-grid">
        <div class="profile-visual animate">
          <div class="action-silhouette">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 400 500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#1a1a1a" />
              <path d="M50 400 L350 100" stroke="#A50000" stroke-width="5" opacity="0.4" />
              <text x="50%" y="50%" dominant-baseline="middle" text-anchor="middle" fill="#fff" font-family="Oswald" font-size="20">TRADITION SILHOUETTE</text>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="profile-info animate">
          <div class="badge">Master Instructor</div>
          <h1>Master <span>Jason Gullion</span></h1>
          <p class="rank">6th Degree Black Belt</p>
          <div class="credentials-row">
            <span>20+ Years Experience</span>
            <span class="dot"></span>
            <span>Vice President</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bio-content section-padding">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-layout">
        <div class="bio-verbatim">
          <p>Jay has been studying Martial Arts for approximately 20 years. He currently holds a 6th degree Black belt in Shotokan, 1st degree in Tae Kwon Do, American Freestyle, and Shorinji Ryu. Jay was the first person ever awarded Master's level by Grandmaster Penny Shannon outside her own family. Among his studies he has earned a Basic Instructors certificate in Modern Arnis under Grandmaster Jeff Delaney. Jay also holds a 3rd degree Black Belt in Shotokan through Rising Sun Martial Arts and a 1st level in Kubudo, under Grandmaster Marc Cantrell. He has been awarded instructors certifactes through both Grandmaster's Penny Shannon and Marc Cantrell. Jay has attended training in Military Arnis under Grandmaster Lisa McManus. Among other styles he has studied is Shito Ryu, Muay Thai, Kung Fu, Aikido, Kali, Iserali combatives, Brazilian Jiu-jitsu, Small Circle Jiu-jitsu. Jay was awarded the 2000 Virginia Karate Alliance state champion title in kata and musical kata, 1st runner up in kumite and weapons.</p>

          <p>Jay has been inducted into the Shanaki Inner Circle Society. He is currently a member in the United States Martial Artist Association and is currently serving as Chief Instructor at Shanaki as well as the corporation's Vice President. Jay has a degree in nursing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar">
          <div class="quick-facts">
            <h4>Quick Facts</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Started Training: ~2006</li>
              <li>Base Style: Shotokan</li>
              <li>Position: Vice President</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <a href={`${base}/instructors`} class="btn btn-outline-dark">Back to Instructors</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  /* Sharing same styles as other profiles */
  .profile-hero { border-bottom: 5px solid var(--color-red); padding-bottom: 0; }
  .profile-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: end; }
  .action-silhouette { border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); background: #1a1a1a; }
  .profile-info { padding-bottom: 4rem; }
  .profile-info h1 { font-size: 4rem; margin: 1rem 0; line-height: 1; }
  .profile-info h1 span { color: var(--color-red); }
  .profile-info .rank { font-size: 1.5rem; color: #888; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .credentials-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: var(--font-heading); color: var(--color-red); }
  .dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: #444; border-radius: 50%; }
  .text-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: 5rem; }
  .bio-verbatim p { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: #333; }
  .sidebar { position: sticky; top: 120px; height: fit-content; }
  .quick-facts { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 2rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-red); }
  .quick-facts h4 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-black); }
  .quick-facts ul { list-style: none; }
  .quick-facts li { margin-bottom: 0.8rem; padding-bottom: 0.8rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .btn-outline-dark { border-color: var(--color-black); color: var(--color-black); width: 100%; text-align: center; }
  .btn-outline-dark:hover { background: var(--color-black); color: var(--color-white); }
  @media (max-width: 992px) { .profile-grid, .text-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; } .profile-info { padding-bottom: 2rem; } .profile-info h1 { font-size: 3rem; } }
</style>



